      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Fix Your Attribution?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-gray-300">Join the agencies transforming their Google Ads performance.</p>
